### sample-4 : use init continaers with sleep 3s and 4s and nginx

---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: sample4
  labels:
    app: web
    purpose: init-container
    
spec:
  initcontainers:
    - name: int-0
      image: alpine
      command:
        - sleep
        - "3s"
    - name: int-1
      image: alpine
      command:
        - sleep
        - "4s"      
  continaers:
    - name: nginx
      image: nginx:latest
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        
K8S supports 3 Quality of services classes for contianers in pod

Guranteed  (if minimum == maximum)
Burstable  ( if minimum < maximum)
Best efforts (Neither set)

---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: best-efforts
  labels:
    app: httpd
    purpose: demo
    
spec:
  containers:
    - name: httpd
      image: httpd:latest
      ports:
        containerPort: 80
        
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: burstable
  labels:
    app: httpd
    purpose: demo
    
spec:
  containers:
    - name: httpd
      image: httpd:latest
      requests:
        cpu: 100m
        memory: 64Mi
      limits:
        cpu: 500m
        memory: 128Mi
      ports:
        containerPort: 80        
        
        
